items.title: Awesome Cassandra
items.content_text:
### Tools / Custom Time Series

*   [ValuStor (⭐53)](https://github.com/Sensaphone/ValuStor) - ValuStor is a key-value pair database solution.
*   [JanuesGraph-Utils (⭐208)](https://github.com/IBM/janusgraph-utils) - Tool to Develop a graph database app.
*   [Scylla-Migrator (⭐66)](https://github.com/scylladb/scylla-migrator) - Migrate data extract using Spark to Scylla, normally from Cassandra.
*   [Cassandra CA Manager (⭐11)](https://github.com/eevans/cassandra-ca-manager) - Create and sign Java keystores.
items.content_html:
